menu "breadboard: bb_led_info"

config BB_LED_INFO_AUTOREGISTER
    bool "Auto-register /api/info \"led\" section via bb_init"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, bb_led_info self-registers the "led" info section through
        bb_init (regular tier, order 1 — after bb_info init at order 2,
        but the section table is open until bb_info_freeze at order 20).
        Consumers that call bb_led_register_info() manually must leave this
        disabled; enabling both double-registers the section. Default n
        preserves backward-compatible manual-register behavior.

        To switch to auto-register: enable this option and remove the
        bb_led_register_info() call from app_main / bringup code.

endmenu
